name: AuthenticationSessionCallback
summary: The callback which is called when the session is completed successfully or canceled by user.

properties.name: callbackURL
properties.summary: The callback-url passed if no error occured, undefined otherwise.

properties.name: error
properties.summary: The error returned if the authentication-session failed, undefined otherwise.

properties.name: success
properties.summary: Returns true if the authentication-session completed successfully, false otherwise.
